00:09:14,215 --> 00:09:19,879
you can like combine all those ideas. Um, so people coming, uh,

197
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:22,641
really fully, you know, into the game,

198
00:09:22,641 --> 00:09:25,564
living out their fantasy of being a Pokemon trainer or.

199
00:09:26,124 --> 00:09:29,127
part of that world, and families will come together,

200
00:09:29,127 --> 00:09:31,589
groups travel from across the country,

201
00:09:31,589 --> 00:09:34,171
carpooling together, people travel

202
00:09:34,171 --> 00:09:34,951
from continent to continent.

203
00:09:34,951 --> 00:09:38,154
So really neat, these have been very successful for us.

204
00:09:38,154 --> 00:09:40,696
Last year we had three million people in total

205
00:09:40,696 --> 00:09:43,378
come to these events, and single day attendance.

206
00:09:43,378 --> 00:09:45,220
At a single event, we've had events

