So just in terms of catching up and looking back retrospectively, a lot of people know

211
00:10:02,455 --> 00:10:07,981
us as a company that helped to pioneer this idea of consumer AR.

212
00:10:07,981 --> 00:10:11,804
The first game we launched was Ingress back in 2012.

213
00:10:12,185 --> 00:10:16,027
Going very well. It's played in a bunch of countries. I think 175 countries around the world.

214
00:10:16,027 --> 00:10:19,868
We've held hundreds of the events of the kind I was describing.

215
00:10:19,868 --> 00:10:22,289
We were doing it with Ingress before Pokémon Go.

216
00:10:22,289 --> 00:10:25,151
We launched a new version of it last year, Ingress Prime.

